| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5547 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1e3b7ea7-b9dc-5dae-9a3f-b389d69dc05e"
